text: Joshua Baret Henderson (born October 25, 1981) is an American actor, model and singer. He is best known for his roles as John Ross Ewing III in the TNT revival of Dallas (2012–2014) and Austin McCann on the ABC television series Desperate Housewives (2006–2007). == References == == Other websites == * Category:1981 births Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Dallas Category:Actors from Tulsa, Oklahoma Category:Models from Texas Category:Models from Oklahoma Category:Singers from Dallas Category:Singers from Tulsa, Oklahoma Category:Living people
